<section class="sec reveal" id="dpa-summary" style="padding-top:36px;padding-bottom:36px;" aria-label="Plain-language summary">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="tldr-prose">
      <span class="eyebrow">The short version</span>
      <p>When we do your books, your financial data stays <strong>yours</strong>. We act as a <strong>processor</strong> &mdash; we handle your data only on your instructions, to deliver the services you engaged us for, and nothing else. We work <strong>inside your own QuickBooks file</strong> as an authorized user; we don&rsquo;t force you to export your data into a system we own, and you can revoke our access anytime. We use encryption, limit who can access your data, and only use vetted sub-processors (like secure file storage) under confidentiality terms. We don&rsquo;t sell your data or use it to train anything. If a data incident ever occurred, we&rsquo;d notify you promptly. The full terms are below and form part of your engagement agreement.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

